POLITICOS COMEDY BRIGADE TO PERFORM OBAMA VS. ROMNEY COMEDY DEBATE

NOVEMBER 4TH AT THE THIRD FLOOR CLUB @ PORTSMOUTH GASLIGHT CO

(NE Patriots BYE Week)

 

The world’s premier political impersonators bring their Election Special to New Hampshire.

Hosted by President Bill Clinton. Moderated by King Maker Donald Trump.

 

Politicos Comedy Brigade(www.politicoscomedy.com), the world-class political comedy troupe whose performers have been featured on Comedy Central and HBO’s Real Time with Bill Maher, is teaming up with Drinkwater Productions, LLC  to bring America’s number one comedic Presidential debate to The Third Floor Club at The Portsmouth Gas Light Co.  on Sunday, November 4th for a Matinee show.

The show features Barack Obama impersonator Maxwell Price (HBO’s Flight of the Conchords, NPR’s This American Life), Mitt Romney impersonator Jim Gossett (The Glenn Beck Program, Michael Savage Show), Bill Clinton impersonator Tim Watters (over 200 appearances on NBC’s The Tonight Show with Jay Leno), and the only Donald Trump impersonator endorsed by the real Donald Trump, John Di Domenico (Disaster Movie, Meet the Spartans).

Renowned for their high profile publicity stunts and prolific appearances on stage, television, new media, and film, Politicos Comedy Brigade will be in town for a matinee show at Third Floor Club at The Portsmouth Gas Light Co. on Sunday, November 4th, located at 64 Market Street, Portsmouth, NH. Doors open at 2:00pm at which time a pub menu will be available to patrons. Show time is 3:00pm.

Tickets are available for $25 each at www.drinkwaterproductions.com, or by calling 855-255-5750.

Politicos Comedy Brigade is the world’s greatest team of impersonators, character actors, and impressionists, featuring comedic portrayals of past, current, and future Presidents along with some of the most recognizable faces in American politics and pop culture today. Visit them at www.politicoscomedy.com
item.name: SHOW CANCELLED-Obama versus Romney Political Comedy Brigade
